snippet.title: [HINDI] BGIS 2024 | GRAND FINALS | Day 3 | BGMI
snippet.description:
Welcome to the GRAND FINALS of the BGIS 2024

Feel the pulse-pounding intensity as the top 16 teams converge on the battleground for a shot at ultimate glory in BGIS history. This is more than just a tournament round, it's the climax of the BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024, where dreams soar and legends are made. With a massive prize pool of INR 2 Crores, the stakes are at their peak.

16 Lan Finalists: GLOBAL ESPORTS, TEAM AARU, X SPARK, iQOO SOUL, FS ESPORTS, VASISTA ESPORTS, TEAM TAMILAS, R4VEN ESPORTS, CARNIVAL GAMING, MOGO ESPORTS, TEAM LIMRA, VENOM GAMING, 8 BIT, TEAM INSANE ESPORTS, INFERNO SQUAD, RECKONING ESPORTS.

snippet.title: Dhilluku Dhuddu - Comedy Scenes | Santhanam Super Hit Counters | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
Kumar and Kajal are in love but her father is against the match and tries to have Kumar killed with the help of Mani. Things go awry when Mani invites Kumar's family to a haunted house. 

Dhilluku Dhuddu  is a 2016 Indian Tamil-language comedy horror film directed by Rambala and produced by Sri Thenandal Films. The film features starring Santhanam and Anchal Singh in the leading roles, while Saurabh Shukla appears in a pivotal role. Featuring music composed by S. Thaman, Dhilluku Dhuddu began production in November 2015 and released on 7 July 2016 to positive response and turned to be successful at box office.[3][4][5] The film was later dubbed in Hindi as Raj Mahal 3 in 2017. The film was dubbed in Telugu as Dammunte Sommera in 2018.[6] The film was remade in Kannada in 2019 as Gimmick starring Ganesh.

Thaman, Dhilluku Dhuddu began production in November 2015 and released on 7 July 2016 to positive response and turned to be successful at box office.[3][4][5] The film was later dubbed in Hindi as Raj Mahal 3 in 2017. The film was dubbed in Telugu as Dammunte Sommera in 2018.[6] The film was remade in Kannada in 2019 as Gimmick starring Ganesh.

Double ISMART First Single out Tomorrow at 4 PM üé∂üî•

#DoubleISMART is an Indian Action Entertainer film, written and directed by Puri Jagannnadh featuring Ram Pothineni in the lead role will be seen in a Massier character than iSmart Shankar. Also stars Sanjay Dutt, Kavya Thapar in the prominent roles. Produced by Puri Jagannadh and Charmme Kaur under Puri Connects, The film will have a much bigger span and will be made with a high budget on a large scale with top-class technical standards. Popatlal grows increasingly anxious while waiting for Inspector Pandey's call to find out if his horoscope matches with the potential bride's. With each passing moment, his impatience mounts. How will Popatlal cope with the suspense and uncertainty surrounding his future?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

This special film showcases the struggle of Sanatan Vijay, a poor boy aspiring to join the police force as a constable. Dedicated to the hardworking youth of the nation who dare to dream, 'Sipahi' aims to uncover their struggle and inspire everyone.
